ygData.messageBody:
Cinda's Charismatic Carrillion sounds like such a good song, it is
really a bummer that it appears to have no/little effect. IMO it is
broken and also IMO should be one of our defining songs.

What I would like to see from the song is the ability to go to places
Bards are not normally able to go, such as the Troll/Orge cities. It
is our function after all to document the history of Norrath,record
the stories of all races, and to bring a song to many different faces.

I will feedback this tonight.


Has anybody else found level 11 to be a bit of a wall? I am finding it
hard going.
